Sinnertwin continued burning the forest, but was plowed over by the
blast from his commander. One of his heads reared back. "I just saying
hello." it snarled, as the other head nipped at something moving on the
ground, anjd disgustingly swallowed it, then a mechanical tongue whiped
around his face, spraying blood around.

Motormaster nodded, and turned to the Stunticons. "MERGE." he shouted,
as he leapt up into the air, his body folding together, making a large
torso area. Wildrider looked at the rest, and laughed, transforming
first to his car mode, then sitting up on his trunk, transforming into a
large leg, Breakdown followed suite.
